And here is a complete list of \fBnoise keywords\fR ignored by
monit:
.PP
\&\fIis\fR, \fIas\fR, \fIare\fR, \fIon(ly)\fR, \fIwith(in)\fR, \fIand\fR, \fIhas\fR,
